QuestData.Title: Skycaller Soltok
QuestData.Description: As if snake-men with swords not be bad enough, they brought a powerful skycaller along.$b$b I hear skycallers can tempt great storms into being. They be to blame for de spires and lightning flying everywhere.$b$bThere be one who wear a bigger feather than most, likely de leader. Calls herself Soltok or something equally hissy.$b$bDon't care. Kill her.
QuestData.PortraitGiverText: Skycaller Soltok commands the Sethrak forces attacking Zuldazar.
